Feature: Simple Multi-Device Screenshot Test\n\n  Take screenshots of multiple device pages to analyze page structure\n\n  @browser @playwright @device-config @debug\n  Scenario: Simple Multi-Device Screenshot Test\n    Given I open a browser to "${base_url}/${page}/${endpoint_id}"\n    And I take a screenshot named "device_${endpoint_id}_debug"\n    And I wait with time: 2, description: Wait 2 seconds for page to fully load\n    And I take a screenshot named "device_${endpoint_id}_final"